courses.Prerequisites: OCI CLI,  Oracle Resource Manager,  Manage custom images,  Network Security Architecture

courses.title: Google Cloud Digital Leader Training
courses.summary: Gain foundational literacy in cloud & digital transformation. Increase your cloud confidence so you can speak with colleagues in technical cloud roles and contribute to informed cloud-related business decisions.
courses.Prerequisites: Google Cloud Fundamentals,  Cloud Computing Fluency,  Digital Transformation Strategy,  Data Innovation,  IT Infrastructure Modernization,  Application Modernization,  Cloud Cost Governance,  Cloud Security Fluency,  Cloud Operational Efficiency

courses.title: Cloud Native Fundamentals
courses.summary: Throughout this course, students will learn how to structure, package, and release an application to a Kubernetes cluster, while using an automated CI/CD pipeline.
courses.Prerequisites: Kubernetes,  Docker,  Cloud Computing Fluency,  Cloud Architecture Model Types,  CI/CD,  Application Development Best Practices,  Argo CD,  Github Actions,  Platform as a Service

courses.title: Cyber-Physical Systems Design & Analysis
courses.summary: This course provides an introduction to cyber-physical systems with an industrial perspective.

courses.title: Differential Equations in Action
courses.summary: Write Python code to find numerical solutions to systems of differential equations. The models you create will fight wildfires, bring spaceships back to earth, and more!
courses.Prerequisites: Math, Differential Equations

courses.title: Self-Driving Fundamentals: Featuring Apollo
courses.summary: Identify key parts of self-driving cars, utilize Apollo HD Map, localization, perception, prediction, planning and control, and start the learning path of building a self-driving car.
courses.Prerequisites: Apollo HD Map, Localization, Perception, Prediction, Planning, Control

courses.title: Product Manager Interview Preparation
courses.summary: Ace your product management interview by understanding how to answer key strategic, technical, and practical product questions.
courses.Prerequisites: Product Management, Interview Preparation, Career Advancement, Product Strategy, Technical Interview

courses.title: Craft Your Cover Letter
courses.summary: Write a compelling narrative that showcases your value to the company.
courses.Prerequisites: Creating a narrative, Targeting your pitch, Communicating value, Career Advancement

courses.title: Refresh Your Resume
courses.summary: Create a targeted resume that gets the attention of recruiters and lands you an interview in tech.
courses.Prerequisites: Resume writing, Company targeting, Storytelling, Career Advancement

courses.title: Strengthen Your LinkedIn Network & Brand
courses.summary: Learn how to excel at networking both in-person and on LinkedIn.
courses.Prerequisites: Personal branding, LinkedIn, Networking, Career Advancement

courses.title: Data Science Interview Prep
courses.summary: Prepare for data science interviews by practicing data analysis, machine learning, and data structure and algorithms questions.
courses.Prerequisites: Interview practice, Common Data Questions, Data Structures, Career Advancement

courses.title: Android Interview Prep
courses.summary: Learn how to respond to common Android and mobile development interview questions.
courses.Prerequisites: Interview practice, Common Android Questions, Whiteboarding

courses.title: Machine Learning Interview Preparation
courses.summary: In this course, you’ll learn exactly what to expect during a machine learning interview.
courses.Prerequisites: Interview practice, Machine Learning, Career Advancement

courses.summary: Answer front-end technical and behavioral interview questions with confidence and poise.

courses.title: Full-Stack Interview Prep
courses.summary: Answer common full stack and web security interview questions with confidence and poise.

courses.title: Data Structures & Algorithms in Swift
courses.summary: Review and practice the skills technical interviewers expect you to know and learn how to explain your Swift solutions.

courses.title: iOS Interview Prep
courses.summary: Answer iOS and mobile development interview questions with confidence and poise.
courses.Prerequisites: Interview practice, Common iOS Questions, Whiteboarding, Career Advancement

courses.title: VR Interview Prep
courses.summary: Learn how to tackle interview questions for technical roles in VR Development.
courses.Prerequisites: Interview practice, Common VR Questions, Whiteboarding, Career Advancement
